title: Arris CMTS: Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arris
license: GPL
distribution:
description:
 This check monitors the Temperature information for several equipment parts in the Arris device.

 You configure upper levels for {WARN}/{CRIT} (default: 40/46)

 The service goes {WARN}/{CRIT} if the temperature exceeds these levels.

 The check uses the CADANT-CMTS-EQUIPMENT-MIB.

item:
 The Cardname

inventory:
 One service is created for each card.

